---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../../../components/PageHeader.astro";
import Section from "../../../components/Section.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Imprint — Premium TV Player"
  description="Legal operator details for Premium TV Player — Belkis Aslani, Freiberg am Neckar, Germany."
>
  <PageHeader
    eyebrow="Legal · § 5 TMG / § 18 MStV"
    title="Imprint"
    lede="Premium TV Player is an independent project currently being prepared for launch. This page publishes the operator details as required by German law."
  />

  <Section>
    <article class="legal-body">
      <p class="legal-callout">
        <strong>Status note.</strong> Premium TV Player is in its pre-launch
        phase. The operator, Belkis Aslani, is in the process of registering a
        sole-proprietor business (Einzelunternehmen) to distribute the app
        commercially in Germany. During this transition, the operator
        information below reflects the private individual legally responsible
        for this website, pursuant to § 5 TMG and § 18 MStV. The imprint will
        be updated with the registered business name, VAT identification
        number and commercial-register entry as soon as the registration
        process is complete.
      </p>

      <h2 class="t-title-large">Operator (Anbieterin)</h2>
      <address class="plain">
        <strong>Belkis Aslani</strong><br />
        Vogelsangstraße 32<br />
        71691 Freiberg am Neckar<br />
        Germany
      </address>

      <h2 class="t-title-large">Contact</h2>
      <address class="plain">
        Email: <a href="mailto:belkis.aslani@gmail.com">belkis.aslani@gmail.com</a><br />
        Phone: <a href="tel:+4917681462526">+49 176 81462526</a>
      </address>

      <h2 class="t-title-large">Responsible for content (§ 18 Abs. 2 MStV)</h2>
      <p>Belkis Aslani, Vogelsangstraße 32, 71691 Freiberg am Neckar, Germany.</p>

      <h2 class="t-title-large">Business registration &amp; VAT ID</h2>
      <p>
        A sole-proprietor business registration (Gewerbeanmeldung per § 14 GewO) and a
        VAT identification number (Umsatzsteuer-Identifikationsnummer per § 27 a UStG)
        are currently being processed. Both entries will be added here as soon as they
        are issued. Until then, any goods or services offered via this website are
        subject to the small-business regulation under § 19 UStG where applicable.
      </p>

      <h2 class="t-title-large">EU dispute resolution</h2>
      <p>
        The European Commission provides a platform for online dispute resolution (OS):
        <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
          https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr/
        </a>.
        We are neither obliged nor willing to participate in dispute-resolution
        proceedings before a consumer arbitration board.
      </p>

      <h2 class="t-title-large">Liability for content</h2>
      <p>
        As a service provider, the operator is responsible for her own content on these
        pages pursuant to § 7 Abs. 1 TMG. Under §§ 8 to 10 TMG, however, the operator is
        not obliged to monitor transmitted or stored third-party information or to
        investigate circumstances that indicate illegal activity. Content will be removed
        promptly once the operator becomes aware of a concrete legal infringement.
      </p>

      <h2 class="t-title-large">Liability for links</h2>
      <p>
        This website contains links to external websites over which the operator has no
        control. No liability is therefore assumed for the external content. The
        respective provider or operator of the linked pages is always responsible for
        their content. Linked pages were checked for legal violations at the time of
        linking; illegal content was not apparent at that time. Permanent content
        monitoring of linked pages is not reasonable without concrete evidence of a
        violation. Links will be removed immediately upon becoming aware of any
        infringement.
      </p>

      <h2 class="t-title-large">Copyright</h2>
      <p>
        The content and works created by the operator on these pages are subject to
        German copyright law. Duplication, processing, distribution and any kind of
        exploitation outside the limits of copyright require the written consent of the
        operator. Downloads and copies of this site are only permitted for private,
        non-commercial use.
      </p>

      <h2 class="t-title-large">Third-party trademarks</h2>
      <p>
        "Android", "Android TV", "Google TV", "Google Play" and the Google Play logo are
        trademarks of Google LLC. This site and the Premium TV Player application are
        independent projects and are not endorsed by, sponsored by, or otherwise
        affiliated with Google LLC.
      </p>
    </article>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-body { max-width: 780px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-l); }
  .legal-body h2 { margin: var(--space-l) 0 0; color: var(--color-on-surface-high); }
  .legal-body p, .legal-body li { margin: 0; color: var(--color-on-surface); }
  .legal-body a { color: var(--color-accent-cyan); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; word-break: break-word; }
  address.plain { font-style: normal; color: var(--color-on-surface); line-height: 1.65; }
  .legal-callout {
    padding: clamp(16px, 3.5vw, 24px);
    border-radius: var(--radius-m);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.35);
    background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.06);
    color: var(--color-on-surface) !important;
  }
</style>
